    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款推箱子游戏。玩家将控制一只可爱的小松鼠收集橡果，帮助它度过寒冷的冬天。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300960/extras/2da9e9f225b1116a379c52d6f95db90a.avif?t=1736825842\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300960/extras_big/2da9e9f225b1116a379c52d6f95db90a.avif?t=1736825842 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏在一般推箱子的基础上，增加了一些独特的设计，包括可移动的障碍，可移除的障碍，以及不同障碍之间的相互作用。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >木头可以推入河中形成桥梁：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300960/extras/14f69c9c0f423d6ddedbad32a365501c.poster.avif?t=1736825842\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300960/extras/14f69c9c0f423d6ddedbad32a365501c.webm?t=1736825842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300960/extras/14f69c9c0f423d6ddedbad32a365501c.mp4?t=1736825842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >野猪可以破坏灌木：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300960/extras/f1fe1c9ef477ddb136b30abe89e24ebe.poster.avif?t=1736825842\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300960/extras/f1fe1c9ef477ddb136b30abe89e24ebe.webm?t=1736825842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300960/extras/f1fe1c9ef477ddb136b30abe89e24ebe.mp4?t=1736825842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏还为不善此类游戏的玩家温馨的提供了谜题答案，只要您能先自己付出一段时间的努力。每关解锁答案所需时间不同，一般是越难时间越长。但是请放心，最多不会超过10分钟</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >右下角的播放按钮可以播放完整答案：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300960/extras/aada330bc7e2d1fa1be1a5cfe4c822d3.avif?t=1736825842\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300960/extras_big/aada330bc7e2d1fa1be1a5cfe4c822d3.avif?t=1736825842 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
